Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah. I'm gonna be away a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:03.28,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Geez, what've you been doing?\NEverybody at school is worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}‘I'm on a really tough case’, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, sorry, Shin'ichi! I have to go or I'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:17.40,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Bye! It's getting colder, so be careful so you don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:26.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't know why, {\blur3}but Ran's been acting weird these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:33.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She's kind of cold over the phone, {\blur3}and she doesn't cry ‘Shin'ichi! Shin'ichi!’ like she used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the weirdest thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I'm going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dinner's on the table. Warm it up in the microwave before you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Uhh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:53.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}...is that she goes out every afternoon and only comes back late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She {\i1}claims{\i0} she's got extra training for the karate club tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But it doesn't really fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She always looks so... {\i1}happy{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What? You've been going to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah. We're about to get the results of my tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you sick, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Maybe. I've been feeling very tired lately.{Kogorō's in saa mode}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You've probably been drinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Exactly! You didn't have to pick us up from school for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's probably nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The doctor told me on the phone\Nto bring my closest relatives along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}H-Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Kogorō Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You have six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm very sorry about this,\Nbut you have six months...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}How could you do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Suddenly telling me that\NI only have six months to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If I have that serious a disease, you should've told me earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Serious disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What I was trying to say was that you have to refrain from drinking alcohol for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}According to your blood test, you've got a case of alcohol-induced cirrhosis of the liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Though it's not too serious yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But you scared me, Dr. Araide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You made me bring my family and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:41.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(320,350)}Yoshiteru Araide (51)\NLocal Practitioner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}With patients like you, who like to drink so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}cooperation from the family is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Just cut down on the amount\Nyou drink each day, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No way! I won't let him drink a single drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You've got a phone call from Sugita-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}She wants you to make a house call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}She's one tough patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's just a gastric ulcer,\Nbut she's so worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}Patient? Yeah, right. More like mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:07.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,350)}Yōko Araide (46)\NYoshiteru's wife
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Please wait a moment. I'm sure he'll be off the phone soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Could I use your toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The public toilet seems to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}On the way, I turned right at the end of the corridor, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That means the examination room must be right up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This house is so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm sorry... I wasn't looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, no. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Here. That should be all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Er, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm Mouri's daughter. He's seeing Dr. Araide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh... Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}I'm the doctor's son, Tomoaki.\NI help my father out here at his clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But I'm going off to work at a hospital in Aomori starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:09.32,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(310,360)}Tomoaki Araide (25)\NYoshiteru's son / Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When are you going to get used to working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And after you begged me to hire you as a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Come on, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You know getting too riled-up is bad for your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Listen up! Screw up again, and you're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}Ugh! I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(310,360)}Hikaru Yasumoto (22)\NHousemaid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Remember to stay away from alcohol if you want a long and happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You even have the same name as that other Kogorō Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Haven't you heard of him?\NHe's a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, no. You see, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What? You're really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, when I saw your name, I did wonder, but I didn't expect that you were really him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You had me fooled completely,\Npretending to have no medical knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why don't you join me for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We can exchange ideas about forensic medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}W-We can't! I've got homework,\Nand Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0} has karate practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, it's fine. Since they're inviting, we might as well go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I can skip practice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}‘Araide Clinic — Closed for the day’
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I knew it. Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You graduated at the top of your class at Tohto Medical School, Tomoaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Isn't that right, Tomoaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I was lucky, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, how about you marry my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I think you'd make a fine couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Come on, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Be careful! The {\i1}chawanmushi{\i0} is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Weren't you going to make arrangements for your class reunion tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're right! I have to call Masae!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{You're free to marry her whenever you like!}Hey, if you ever think it over, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We could be like Holmes and Watson!\NTogether, we can solve any mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I think I'll pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm not sure a detective and a doctor would make a good pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The real job of a doctor isn't to find the murderer by performing an autopsy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}but to save the victim from death in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You've got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I don't know which one would be Holmes though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right, Ran-{\i1}nee{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}...{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I wonder what's taking your husband so long.\NHis clinic should've closed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}That man always takes a bath before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:16.32,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(310,360)}Mitsu Araide (74)\NTomoaki's Grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\blur1}He dirties the water for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Grandma! Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, traditionally the breadwinner of the family enters the bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Breadwinner, my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He's the one who married into my family, so he's got no right to put on airs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're the only blood relation\NI've got left in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But you're leaving home next month...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're practically {\i1}telling{\i0} me to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Er, what about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{You strangers can eat together!}I have no interest in eating around strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Please don't let her bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Grandma's been in a bad mood since Dad changed the bath and toilet to Western style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Western style?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:09.42,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1\fsp-0.8}She was very annoyed when he replaced our antique cypress bath with a modern tub and shower curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}She says it's a dishonour against the house's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, she sure is an energetic old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No way, a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I think it's just this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The lights are on next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Um, I think there's a flashlight\Nin that drawer over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll go take a look at the circuit breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Watch your step, Hikaru-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.44,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We've got a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, is it raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, it's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, sorry! I mistook you for Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:24.10,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}And about the fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right. I think ¥30,000 is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are the lights back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Silly girl! Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I think we should check on Dad in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I bet he's upset about all the lights going off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm worried about his heart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What caused the blackout, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It could've been a short-circuit, or too much electricity being used at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That came from the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If you do, you'll get an electric shock too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Electric shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's an extension cord\Nconnected to this electric razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'll try to resuscitate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Mother, go get the drip with the cardiotonic!{cat: Go get the heart medicine!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hikaru-{\i1}san{\i0}, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, and call the police, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:02.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It looks like he was shocked when that electric cord fell in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:06.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He could've been using that mirror over the bathtub to shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But why would he shave in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm sorry to report that Yoshiteru Araide-{\i1}san{\i0} has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He did have a weak heart to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-This... This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In what state did you find Yoshiteru-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He was slumped in the bathtub\Nwith his head facing this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But why'd he use an electric razor in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It was a habit of my husband's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He always did it while keeping his guests waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He even got a mirror that wouldn't fog up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But wasn't it strange for him to take a bath and keep his guests waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Dad loved taking baths. He always took a bath in the morning and before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He thought it was important\Nfor doctors to keep clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}He deserved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This was divine retribution\Nfor not listening to Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Chiaki decided to punish him from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Who's Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}My mother. She died in a car accident four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}She always told him not to use the electric razor in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}She said it was dangerous to use it with the cord attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then, Yōko-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm his second wife.\NWe got married two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Chiaki and I were in the same\Nclass at nursing school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and she often talked about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Inspector! Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If you stand up to shave yourself in front of the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}the socket of this extension cord\Ncomes right to the edge of the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}This sure is risky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Where were all of you\Nwhen the blackout occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}In the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}My mother-in-law wasn't, {\blur1}but I saw her climb up the stairs at the other end of the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then Yoshiteru-{\i1}san{\i0} was using the electric razor in the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and accidentally pulled the cord into the bathtub, causing a deadly electric shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A simple accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey! No fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But I'm so confused, I've got a splitting headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The man who died was shaving himself standing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and Takagi-{\i1}san{\i0} was pretending to be him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then when he felt the shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}he should've fallen over like Takagi-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwith his head on this side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But that man's head was facing the other way! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{Hey, the kid's got a point.}That could've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}While Yoshiteru-{\i1}san{\i0} was shaving himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}he noticed that the cord was\Nabout to fall into the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}so he turned around to pick it up, but ended up pulling it into the bath instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then he happened to touch the handrail, electricity flowed through him with a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}and he fell into the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Something like that, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{Not bad, old man.}Not too shabby, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, don't play with that razor, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Isn't it an important piece of evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Play? I'm just holding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then was it you, Takagi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh? I didn't mess with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then the man from forensics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-I just took photos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Weird. Then who could've played around with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The razor's switched off! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What's this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Y-Yes, it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If this man died of an electric shock while shaving, the razor should be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Detective Takagi must've pushed the power switch when he fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Huh? I thought we unplugged that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We did. I'm holding the plug now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see! This is a rechargeable shaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then why was it turned off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{It wasn't on when you found the body, was it?}Nobody touched it since you found the body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Maybe it's the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Somebody didn't want the sound of the shaver to be heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\i1}Who{\i0} didn't want {\i1}who{\i0} to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{How would I know? I'm just a dumb kid!}Beats me! I'm just making guesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Maybe somebody wanted to sneak the cord in the tub while Yoshiteru-{\i1}san{\i0} was taking his bath
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}without catching his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If somebody did that, he'd have noticed it even without the noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And everybody has an alibi during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:06.87,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,{\blur1}Come to think of it, when the light came on, it went off again for a moment before coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hikaru-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're the one who reset the breaker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Did you by any chance flip it twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I thought I might have flipped the wrong switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A different breaker shut off,\Nso I quickly flipped it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I-I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Inspector, the second time the breaker jumped, could it have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The killer could create some sort of timer to cause a blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}then use the opportunity to sneak into the bathroom and drop the cord into the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Then any one of those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}...could have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Hey, why are you whispering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:19:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Never mind! I was wondering if we could hear what you were doing during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Didn't we just tell you our alibis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you saying there's a murderer among us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We just want to be sure, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}So you were on the phone the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}From before the blackout to the time the lights turned back on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I was talking on the phone next to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I was talking to my friend Masae about our class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, and my call waiting went off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But the person on the other end just hung up without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Takagi! Go check that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}During the blackout, I dug out the torch and handed it to Hikaru-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}After that, I was in the kitchen the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Can you prove that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Tomoaki-{\i1}san{\i0} was here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}From the point when Hikaru-{\i1}san{\i0} went to reset the breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I grabbed onto Tomoaki-{\i1}san{\i0} the whole time. I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I told you, didn't I? I mistook him for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Next, Mitsu-{\i1}san{\i0}. Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When the lights went off, I'd just finished climbing the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I groped my way back to my room upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But when the lights went on, you came back down the stairs to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I felt a presence just as I was about to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Like someone was just outside my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Someone else may have\N been inside the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I followed the presence downstairs and discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It was only the sound of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And finally, Hikaru-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I went to reset the circuit breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I'm not used to this house yet,\Nso I got lost at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And you didn't see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}No. Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I was wondering why you kept touching your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You still put up with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A burn mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Excuse me. Can I go down to the clinic to treat her wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Sure. But go with the\N detective waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Want to keep watch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, and one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're the only one who left this house today, from 5 to 7 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I coach the high school basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Their coach used to teach me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:22:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}but he broke a bone and asked me if I could take over for him until he recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A doctor {\i1}and{\i0} a sports coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If you don't believe me, ask Ran-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}The team I'm coaching is at Teitan High School, the same school she goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You know Tabuchi-{\i1}sensei{\i0},\Nthe basketball coach, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:25.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Is that why Ran went out to karate practice at school every evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:31.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It couldn't be!
