Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:59.71,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, what is this thing called love?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:04.98,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Even if you're blindly searching through darkness for warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:11.16,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Someday you'll surely find a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:23.38,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, if love were to take form, it'd be round like an egg
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:34.72,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, so right now, speak your first cry in these hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:43.11,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Even with faked bravery you can still be reckless
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.11,0:23:48.48,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, you may not have much courage now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:59.45,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, but I'll gather and raise it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Could you go take a look at the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But why another blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Come to think of it, that man said he was running an experiment in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Don't tell me that Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're the killer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}On the next Conan: ‘The Blind Spot in the Darkness (Part II)’!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Next Conan's Hint: Burn wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.66,0:24:41.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\pos(314,410)\1a&H1F&\fnSegoe\3c&H7F001F&\3a&H7F&\fscx100\bord2\shad0\fs28}Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.04,0:24:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.76,0:24:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}Not good... Ran's feelings are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.68,0:24:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}Huh? Were you there, Shin'ichi?
